<body id="body" class="bg-white text-gray-900 leading-relaxed">
{{> header_amp}}

<main class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-20 py-16">
  <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

  <ul class="mb-8 text-gray-600">
    <li><strong>Effective Date:</strong> May 19th, 2025</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
    <strong>At stakers.space, your privacy is important to us.</strong>
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    We do <strong>not</strong> collect, store, or process any personal data unless you voluntarily provide 
    it through your Stakers.space account. Even there, everything sensitive is client-side encrypted, 
    meaning we do not know the real data values.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-10">
    This Privacy Policy describes how Stakers.space ("we", "our", or "us") collects, uses, 
    and protects your personal information when you visit our website.
  </p>

  <!-- Section 1 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li><strong>In guest mode:</strong> we do not collect any data nor cookies for analytics purposes.</li>
    <li>
      <p class="mb-2"><strong>In registered user mode:</strong> we collect:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li><i>Email address</i> (required for account creation and login)</li>
        <li><i>Encrypted user data</i> (optional – encrypted on your device before storage)</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-4">
        We do <strong>not</strong> collect any additional personal information unless you voluntarily 
        submit it. Most entered data is <strong>end-to-end encrypted</strong> and unreadable to us.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6 mb-3">1.2 Encryption and Data Privacy</h3>
      <p class="mb-3">All user-provided data (except email) is encrypted <strong>client-side</strong>, meaning:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li>Data is encrypted in your browser before being sent to our servers</li>
        <li>We <strong>do not store</strong> encryption keys</li>
        <li>We <strong>cannot decrypt</strong> your data – only you can</li>
        <li>
          If there are any data that cannot use client-side encryption due to technical reasons, 
          we clearly note that and explain risk mitigation. Filling such data is always optional.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-4">This ensures that even if our systems are compromised, your encrypted data remains secure.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <!-- Section 2 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li>We use a single <strong>technical cookie</strong> solely for authentication (to keep you logged in).</li>
    <li>We do <strong>not</strong> use analytics, tracking cookies, advertising pixels, or third-party trackers.</li>
  </ul>

  <!-- Section 3 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li>To manage user accounts and logins</li>
    <li>To securely store encrypted content associated with your account</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mb-8">
    We do <strong>not</strong> share your data with third parties, sell it, or use it for marketing purposes.
  </p>

  <!-- Section 4 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Your Rights</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li>You can delete your account at any time. This removes your email and all encrypted data.</li>
    <li>For access, correction, or deletion requests, contact us at <a href="mailto:stakersspace@proton.me" class="text-emerald-600 hover:underline">stakersspace@proton.me</a>.</li>
  </ul>

  <!-- Section 5 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Hosting & Infrastructure</h2>
  <p class="mb-8">
    Our service may use standard infrastructure providers (e.g., hosting, Cloudflare) for security and performance, 
    but we do not analyze server logs for tracking.
  </p>

  <!-- Section 6 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p class="mb-12">We may occasionally update this policy. The latest version will always be available on this page.</p>

  <p class="text-lg">
    If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at 
    <a href="mailto:stakersspace@proton.me" class="text-emerald-600 hover:underline">stakersspace@proton.me</a>.
  </p>
</main>

